      "id": "ff657c88-8e40-4fc7-9834-e8047c47d653",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper seems to be a review about assessment strategies and how AI can be used to automate this task and improve student outcomes. The work starts with a review of assessment strategies, it seems, and follows up how AI can be used as part of them. ",
